<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">Last Updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>
          At Rails Template App, we strive to provide the best service possible. We understand that sometimes
          things don't work out as planned. This Refund Policy explains our policies regarding refunds for
          subscription payments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">2. Subscription Refunds</h2>
        <p>
          We offer a <strong>7-day money-back guarantee</strong> for all new subscriptions. If you are not satisfied
          with our service within the first 7 days of your initial subscription, you may request a full refund.
        </p>
        <p>
          After the initial 7-day period, subscription payments are non-refundable. However, you may cancel your
          subscription at any time, and you will continue to have access to the service until the end of your current billing cycle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">3. How to Request a Refund</h2>
        <p>To request a refund within the 7-day guarantee period:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Contact our support team at <a href="mailto:saanskarastudios@gmail.com">saanskarastudios@gmail.com</a></li>
          <li>Include your account email address and subscription details</li>
          <li>Provide a brief explanation of why you're requesting a refund</li>
          <li>We will process your request within 3-5 business days</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">4. Refund Processing Time</h2>
        <p>
          Once your refund request is approved, it will be processed within 5-10 business days. The refund will be
          credited to the original payment method used for the purchase.
        </p>
        <p>
          Please note that depending on your financial institution, it may take an additional 5-10 business days
          for the refund to appear in your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">5. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>
          You may cancel your subscription at any time through your account settings. When you cancel:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your subscription will remain active until the end of your current billing cycle</li>
          <li>You will continue to have full access to all features until that date</li>
          <li>You will not be charged for subsequent billing cycles</li>
          <li>No refund will be provided for the remaining time in your current billing cycle (unless within the 14-day guarantee period)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">6. Plan Changes</h2>
        <p>
          If you upgrade your plan during a billing cycle, you will be charged a prorated amount for the upgraded
          plan for the remainder of your billing cycle.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you downgrade your plan, the change will take effect at the start of your next billing cycle. No
          refund will be provided for the difference in cost for the current billing cycle.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">7. Exceptions</h2>
        <p>Refunds will not be provided in the following circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>After the 7-day money-back guarantee period has expired</li>
          <li>For partial months of service</li>
          <li>If your account has been terminated due to violation of our Terms of Service</li>
          <li>For charges more than 60 days old</li>
          <li>If you have previously received a refund for the same subscription type</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">8. Disputed Charges</h2>
        <p>
          If you believe you have been charged in error, please contact our support team immediately before
          initiating a chargeback with your credit card company. We will work with you to resolve any billing
          issues promptly.
        </p>
        <p>
          Initiating a chargeback without first contacting us may result in the immediate suspension of your account.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">9. Service Interruptions</h2>
        <p>
          In the event of extended service interruptions or downtime caused by us, we may provide credits or
          refunds on a case-by-case basis. Service interruptions of less than 24 hours are not eligible for refunds.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">10. Annual Subscriptions</h2>
        <p>
          Annual subscriptions are subject to the same 7-day money-back guarantee. After 14 days, annual
          subscriptions are non-refundable. You may cancel your annual subscription at any time, but no prorated
          refund will be provided.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify this Refund Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately
          upon posting to this page. Your continued use of the service after any changes constitutes acceptance of
          the new Refund Policy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-5">
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">12. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about our Refund Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> saanskarastudios@gmail.com<br>
          <strong>Address:</strong> Ottawa, ON, Canada
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-5">
        <%= link_to "â† Back to Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-outline-secondary" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
